snippet: The Royals are sticking with left-hander Jason Vargas and the Orioles with right-hander Miguel Gonzalez for Game 4 of their AL Championship Series on Wednesday....

headline.print_headline: Royals' Vargas, Orioles' Gonzalez to Start Game 4
headline.main: Royals' Vargas, Orioles' Gonzalez to Start Game 4

lead_paragraph: The Royals are sticking with left-hander Jason Vargas and the Orioles with right-hander Miguel Gonzalez for Game 4 of their AL Championship Series on Wednesday.
